data.description: Four bedrooms/three baths in the heart of Neosho? That's right! Not only that but it is on nearly a .5 acre lot! So much room both inside and out, just waiting for you to call it home. The two living rooms (one upstairs and one downstairs)  each have their own fireplace. The walkout basement leads to your fully fenced backyard. Set up your personal tour today!
